snippet.title: Atari Shark Jaws arcade cabinet (1975)
snippet.description:
Here is my Shark Jaws arcade cabinet working.
Made by Atari in 1975 under the name "Horror Games".
Both screen & PCB have been fixed.
Screen : some stupid guy replaced an important inductance by a simple wire (???).
PCB : external shortcut created a partially isolated track where the edge connector fits.

Horizontal bar is a video record artefact, it does not display.
